Simply create a bookmark. Edit the bookmark, and place this code in the URL. Then simply use by clicking on the bookmar. Each click picks a different tool. Wait 2 seconds for the tool to engage, then click again. You have 3 seconds for each tool to continue to use. There is a formater, a colorer, and a deleter. You can use the deleter by running it, then holding ctrl click to delete an element, alt click to resize it, shift-ctrl-click to stick to top left, and alt ctrl click to stick the element to bottom right. Useful for formatting a site to study and/or make more real estate space to read.
